Question: Why this person standing so far from the court?

Reference Answer: skating

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/569432.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='court')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='person')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX1)
BOX2=LOC(image=IMAGE1,object='court')
ANSWER0=COUNT(box=BOX2)
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'far' if {ANSWER0} > 0 else 'close'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER1)
```
